    - target: {fileID: 6563504826612088725, guid: 30c6f40278f2a98469fe98cc26332de9, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'The stats are: MORALE: this is your "HP", keep an eye on it because
        depending on the result of the match, this value changes and if it reaches
        zero, well, your career on that team is over. FRONT OFFICE: Responsible for
        the team''s "operations". Trades, contract negotiations and training and
        FAN SUPPORT: represents the amount of SP Skills you have and gives that little
        push to help a player stay'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
