  m_text: "And finally, here are the team stats. Teams start with a set of unique
    values, after all, each institution is different from the other. But don't worry,
    throughout the season these values \u200B\u200Bwill change over the weeks. Don't
    worry, as a good assistant, I will explain this to you soon."
